ygData.msgSnippet: Head to Overthere till about lvl 23 24 then either head to WW or to FM  (warsilk woods, Frontier Mnts.)  You can bank buy and sell in Overthere.  In Overthere
ygData.messageBody:
Head to Overthere till about lvl 23 24 then either head to WW or to FM  (warsilk woods, Frontier Mnts.)  You can bank buy and sell in Overthere.  In Overthere you will be hunting outside the south entrance of the outpost.. (i think) can't miss the creatuer they are much smaller than the rest and will con blue or maybe even still at 20...
 
Thats all for my advice..
 
Aumne Reginamortis 44th Necro Nodcet Nife
